&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location:&lt;/strong&gt; Montgomery, AL (Hybrid)&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Reports To:&lt;/strong&gt; Regional Director/Director of Operations&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Position Summary&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;The Business Development &amp;amp; Operations Coordinator plays a key role in growing and supporting our commercial janitorial business. This position combines business development with account management and operational support to drive new client acquisition while ensuring exceptional service delivery for existing commercial accounts.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;The ideal candidate is a self-starter who enjoys building relationships, solving problems, and delivering outstanding customer experiences. This individual will partner with clients and Certified Business Owners to maintain service excellence, strengthen customer relationships, and support continued business growth.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Essential Responsibilities&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Business Development&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul data-spread=&quot;false&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and pursue new commercial business opportunities within the assigned territory.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Generate leads through networking, prospecting, referrals, and cold outreach.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct sales presentations and recommend customized janitorial and facility service solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop proposals, negotiate contracts, and close new business opportunities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain an active sales pipeline and accurately track leads, opportunities, and customer interactions within the CRM system.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Meet or exceed established sales and revenue goals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Account Management &amp;amp; Operations&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul data-spread=&quot;false&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as the primary point of contact for assigned commercial accounts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate daily service operations with Certified Business Owners to ensure contract expectations are met.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct routine customer visits, quality assurance inspections, and brand standards audits.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Address customer concerns promptly and implement corrective actions when needed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage contract renewals, service modifications, and special project requests.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build strong relationships with customers to support long-term retention and satisfaction.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Customer Experience&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul data-spread=&quot;false&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deliver responsive, professional, and proactive customer service.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain regular communication with clients to ensure service expectations are consistently met.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Gather customer feedback and identify opportunities to improve service delivery.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support customer retention through relationship management and operational excellence.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Reporting &amp;amp; Market Awareness&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul data-spread=&quot;false&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor local market trends, competitor activity, and industry developments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prepare reports on sales activity, operational performance, customer satisfaction, and account status.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide recommendations to improve processes, customer experience, and business growth.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Qualifications&lt;/h2&gt;
