&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated experience working closely with brand leadership, their teams and portfolio leadership&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Should show a strong understanding of the overall development process&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to travel approximately 30-40%&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with CRM platforms, preferably HubSpot&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
