&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;span data-teams=&quot;true&quot;&gt;The estimated compensation range for this position is $105,000 to $130,000 annually. Actual compensation for the position is based on a variety of factors, including, but not limited to years of experience, skills, qualifications, and geographic location.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
